921
01:14:24,616 --> 01:14:26,564
Tarik, Deke, tarik!

922
01:14:26,654 --> 01:14:27,893
Tarik?

923
01:14:28,751 --> 01:14:32,063
Oh, aku sedang menariknya!
Aku sedang menariknya!

