01:17:30,470 --> 01:17:31,917
Aku harus membawanya masuk.

959
01:17:32,741 --> 01:17:34,184
Dimengerti.

960
01:17:37,909 --> 01:17:39,150
Ya Tuhan,

961
01:17:39,881 --> 01:17:42,020
Jangan biarkan hal
ini terjadi padaku.

962
01:17:44,217 --> 01:17:46,253
Oke. Oke.

